Every now and then I want to keep popping in here to tell anyone who's reluctant (and reading a dozen pages of comments to get convinced, lol) that this is a VERY GOOD copy of the film. It is very unlikely that you'll find a better copy until the dvd / bluray rips come out.

No ads, no audience, and except for about 4 seconds at the very beginning of the film, no camera obstructions. Clear audio and clear picture with nothing too dark to see. Ignore the idiots that are giving this a 2 or saying it's completely unwatchable. Fucking ridiculous.

